/symbol/BIGC/earnings\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BIGC/earnings\" target=\"_blank\">better than expected</a> third fiscal quarter earnings in November. BigCommerce has seen a post-pandemic slowdown in its revenue growth, but the e-Commerce platform continues to have traction in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741636-bigcommerce-holdings-growing-e-commerce-venture-at-a-cheap-price", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 08:58:55"}, {"id": "4741632", "title": "Vigil Neuroscience: Down On A Competitor's Failure", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Medicine costs concept\" data-id=\"1886168190\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(