<p>Because of the rise in the dividend pay-out ratio and higher non-accruals in the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/912018754/image_912018754.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741626-stellus-capital-stock-12-percent-yield-risk-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 07:06:41"}, {"id": "4741625", "title": "Synovus Financial: Series E Dividends Provide Best Yield Despite Premium Price", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323945865/image_1323945865.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Synovus Financial Corp. building, Spartanburg\" data-id=\"1323945865\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6368px\" height=\"4480px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323945865/image_1323945865.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323945865/image_1323945865.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323945865/image_1323945865.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323945865/image_1323945865.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323945865/image_1323945865.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323945865/image_1323945865.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323945865/image_1323945865.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1323945865/image_1323945865.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J. Michael Jones</p></figcaption></f